{
  "_comment": [
    "Registry for prep_features_private.py (the secured-box orchestrator). ADJUST paths,",
    "flags, and output specs to your environment. Command tokens are substituted with",
    "{python} {script} {input} {output} {work} {scripts}.",
    "{input} is the input-data root; the NTD monthly workbooks sit loose in {input} itself",
    "(ntd_anchor_builder scans --data-root non-recursively), while the TIDES exports live in",
    "the {input}/tides topic subfolder.",
    "{output} is each script's own output subdir, collected to attribute its tables.",
    "{work}/out/<script_stem>/ exposes an upstream script's outputs to a downstream one:",
    "otp_by_route consumes otp_monthly_tides' panel that way.",
    "GOVERNANCE: unlike the public registry, the NTD dependent variable and the supply",
    "predictors ARE shipped here on purpose -- this side has no leakage boundary. The anchor",
    "breaks out all three service days on a daily-average basis (weekday/saturday/sunday x",
    "avg_ntd_boardings/avg_revenue_hours/avg_revenue_miles + service_days); the OLS targets",
    "weekday_avg_ntd_boardings. The route-level rollups (NTD cross-section anchor + OTP +",
    "runtime) merge into one route_id bundle (the table the OLS/ML models read); the runtime",
    "route x month panel becomes its own bundle for the future monthly-change model.",
    "IGNORE CONVENTION: an output described with an empty keep_cols list is deliberately",
    "dropped from bundling. otp_monthly_processed.csv is marked that way because it is an",
    "intermediate (otp_by_route reduces it) rather than a model feature."
  ],
  "scripts": [
    {
      "script": "ntd_anchor_builder.py",
      "cmd": ["{python}", "{script}",
              "--data-root", "{input}",
              "--output-dir", "{output}",
              "--grain", "cross_section"],
      "outputs": [
        {"file": "ntd_anchor.csv", "join_keys": ["route_id"],
         "keep_cols": ["weekday_avg_ntd_boardings", "weekday_avg_revenue_hours",
                       "weekday_avg_revenue_miles", "weekday_service_days",
                       "saturday_avg_ntd_boardings", "saturday_avg_revenue_hours",
                       "saturday_avg_revenue_miles", "saturday_service_days",
                       "sunday_avg_ntd_boardings", "sunday_avg_revenue_hours",
                       "sunday_avg_revenue_miles", "sunday_service_days"]}
      ]
    },
    {
      "script": "otp_monthly_tides.py",
      "cmd": ["{python}", "{script}",
              "--stop-visits", "{input}/tides/stop_visits.csv",
              "--trips-performed", "{input}/tides/trips_performed.csv",
              "--output-dir", "{output}"],
      "outputs": [
        {"file": "otp_monthly_processed.csv", "join_keys": [], "keep_cols": []}
      ]
    },
    {
      "script": "otp_by_route.py",
      "cmd": ["{python}", "{script}",
              "--otp-processed", "{work}/out/otp_monthly_tides/otp_monthly_processed.csv",
              "--output-dir", "{output}",
              "--window-months", "12",
              "--normalize"],
      "outputs": [
        {"file": "otp_by_route.csv", "join_keys": ["route_id"],
         "keep_cols": ["pct_on_time"]}
      ]
    },
    {
      "script": "route_runtime_tides.py",
      "cmd": ["{python}", "{script}",
              "--stop-visits", "{input}/tides/stop_visits.csv",
              "--trips-performed", "{input}/tides/trips_performed.csv",
              "--output-dir", "{output}",
              "--window-months", "12",
              "--normalize"],
      "outputs": [
        {"file": "route_runtime_by_route.csv", "join_keys": ["route_id"],
         "keep_cols": ["runtime_mean_min"]},
        {"file": "route_runtime_monthly.csv", "join_keys": ["route_id", "month"],
         "keep_cols": ["runtime_mean_min", "runtime_median_min", "runtime_std_min", "n_obs"]}
      ]
    }
  ],
  "outputs": [
    {"file": "ntd_anchor.csv", "join_keys": ["route_id"],
     "keep_cols": ["weekday_avg_ntd_boardings", "weekday_avg_revenue_hours",
                   "weekday_avg_revenue_miles", "weekday_service_days",
                   "saturday_avg_ntd_boardings", "saturday_avg_revenue_hours",
                   "saturday_avg_revenue_miles", "saturday_service_days",
                   "sunday_avg_ntd_boardings", "sunday_avg_revenue_hours",
                   "sunday_avg_revenue_miles", "sunday_service_days"]},
    {"file": "otp_by_route.csv", "join_keys": ["route_id"],
     "keep_cols": ["pct_on_time"]},
    {"file": "route_runtime_by_route.csv", "join_keys": ["route_id"],
     "keep_cols": ["runtime_mean_min"]}
  ]
}
